<br>
1) Cloak has been in game since start of the game, there's lot of them floatin around (no pun intended). You can buy a MQ from those who got the cloak at level 30 back in the days, not really hard.<br>
<br>
2) PoH staff has been upgraded when it got put on magi, would you still rather kill Inno for it like I did? trust me, you wouldn't. It's the only real bottleneck of mage epic (crowns can be farmed till hell freezes over), and without it epic would be as common as rogue freebringer.<br>
